Jis gali me ghar Tumhara tha,
Badal liya hamne rasta tha,

Ab us nukkad pe nahi aate hai,
jaha se didar tumhare ho jate hai|

Kabhi Ashikana mijaj tha hamara,
Aapke pyar me Deewana naam tha hamara,

Pahle tum meri nasseb thi,
Dil ke kitne karib thi,

Aapka yun milna aur bichad jana,
Han kah ke fir mukar jana |

Dekh tujhe chhat ke munder pe,
Daud aata tha tere dar pe |

Bhid me akeli najar aati ho,
Tanhai me sirf tum yaad aati ho |

Aajkal ishare samajh nahi aate,
Tumhare naam ab hontho pe nahi aate |


Tumne dil ka darwaja khola tha,
Ab Juda na honge tumne bola tha |

Biti bate tumhe ab yaad nahi aati,
vo bewaqt ki call ab nahi satati |

Vo pyasi nigahe tumhe dhundhti hai,
Tanha rate tumhe pukarti hain | 
